extendedInfo.description: LEARN ABOUT YOURSELF & FRIENDS!Not For Entertainment--For Self-Help and Self-Improvement (See Terms of Use below)How Compatible Is Your Relationship?***Both you and your friend can take the tests and obtain compatibility info when you compare your results.Email or post your scores on Facebook to share your scores and compare with friends.PURPOSE: To help discuss and analyze relationships.NOTE: This app contains the same tests as Know Yourself Personality Test but has expanded compatibility results to focus on relationship issues.This app includes over 30 tests covering more than 90 personality characteristics:*Personality analysis*For self knowledge--your personal psychology*For self-improvement/self-help*For love and dating compatibility--find out issues that could cause problems in your relationship*For understanding friendships, relationships--quiz others*Examine self-esteem, work ethic, mental health and much more*Based upon psychological research*Links to CBT (cognitive-behavioral therapy) self-improvement articles and other questionnaires at ExcelAtLife.comTests Included:**Comprehensive Personality Test--45 traits**How Social Are You?**Are You A Leader?**Are You Socially Skilled?**How Happy Are You?**Are You Conscientious?**Perfectionist or Efficient?**How Rational Are You?**What Is Your Emotional IQ?**Are You Likeable?**Do You Cope Well?**Intellectual Style**How Insightful Are You?**How Creative Are You?**How Romantic Are You?**Honesty On These Tests?**Do You Have Anxiety?**Do You Have Depression?**Your Work Style**How Optimistic Are You?**What Is Your Self-Concept?**Do You Forgive Easily?**Do You Have Anger Problems?**Self-Control Problems?**How Persistent Are You?**Internal or External Control?**Do You Have Fear Avoidance?**Do You Live Life Fully?**How Stressed Are You?**Are You Ambitious?**How Do You Handle A Crisis?New Tests Will Be Added On Updates!This app is based upon research in personality psychology and sponsored by a clinical psychologist specializing in cognitive-behavioral therapy (CBT). It is meant for self-help and personality assessment for personal improvement and determining relationship compatibility issues.TERMS OF USE**This app is not for entertainment but for furthering understanding of yourself and your relationships.**There are risks to self-knowledge such as, but not limited to, emotional discomfort or confusion and making decisions that affect your life and others. You assume responsibility for these risks.**The personality test results, audios, articles, and other info are for personal information only and should not be construed as professional advice, therapy, or instruction. **There is no guarantee of validity or accuracy and no action or inaction should be taken based solely on the contents of this information.**You should consult an appropriate health professional on any matter relating to your health and well-being.**You should have a proper medical diagnosis before assuming that you are experiencing any clinical health conditions such as, but not limited to, depression or anxiety disorders based on any information provided here.   	**The audios should not be listened to while driving or any other activity in which you should be alert. 	**If you use this information to make major decisions about your life, you should use under the guidance of an experienced therapist or other professional.**If you send your results to others or post on Facebook you no longer have control over your privacy.**The app developer collects usage data to improve this app to enhance your experience. It will not be released to anyone. You may opt out of sending this data in Menu>Setting

reviews.title: excellent app
reviews.comment: app takes up little memory yet provides in-depth insight into the traits which most affect our relationships. almost as good as having your own therapist
reviews.author: Kristy GH

reviews.title: Excellent!
reviews.comment: This app is an extremely beneficial tool for those of us who desire to challenge our personal belief about our personality. IMO, by developing that knowledge and acquiring a different perspective on who or what we believe we can become an increasingly balanced and happy individual.
reviews.author: Keely Gerlach

reviews.title: Amazing.
reviews.comment: Did the comprehensive personality test and now I can finally describe myself and I feel more confident about who I am. I feel closer to myself. Thank you for this beautiful app. <3
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: To thy own self be true & learn something . . .
reviews.comment: This app is great for learning about yourself & others! Take tests & get good psychological results. (My Major in University) Use this as a tool to learn about yourself, help navigate your thoughts & work at becoming a better you. Let a friend take the test on your phone to do the same or to learn about each other. This is accademic & lots of fun too! Right now I can\'t find a way to post this to my wall for maximum sharing, but hopefully that will change soon. In any case, live, learn & enjoy this app! D.B.
